products.name: Zion Williamson Air Jordan
products.description1: x Zion Williamson Air Jordan 1 Low OG 'Voodoo' sneakers
products.description2: The Air Jordan 1 Low “Voodoo” is a special New Orleans-inspired colourway of the classic sneaker that was released alongside basketball star Zion Williamson’s Nike Zion 2 of the same nickname. This sneaker is inspired by voodoo dolls, a fixture of New Orleans’ lore.
